Searching bills

NOTE: Bill searches only return a limited set of bill attributes, a find must be done to retrieve the full bill information

By keyword and state
GovKit::OpenStates::Bill.search('residential', :state => 'ia')

By keyword, state and chamber
GovKit::OpenStates::Bill.search('residential', :state => 'ia', :chamber => 'upper')

Retrieving a bill

By state, session and bill id
rb2 = GovKit::OpenStates::Bill.find('IA', '2011-2012', 'HF 2115')
